graph TD
    subgraph Fuentes_y_Seguridad
    S[Logs/DB/API] -->|Auth: HashiCorp Vault| P[Python Scraper / Airflow]
    P -->|Hashing PII: SHA-256| L[S3 Landing Zone]
    end

    subgraph Refineria_de_Datos_LowCost
    L -->|Carga| D[(DuckDB / Postgres)]
    D -->|Transforma: dbt-core| T[Data Marts / Gold Zone]
    T -->|Valida: Great Expectations| Q{Data Quality OK?}
    end

    subgraph Entrega_de_Valor_Business
    Q -->|Si| BI[Streamlit / Looker Studio]
    Q -->|No| W[Alertas: Wazuh / Slack]
    BI -->|Decisión| B[[Aumentar Ingresos / Bajar Costos]]
    end

    style B fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Q fill:#f96,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
